cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction from a single image and uses image-based supervision. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper deals with generating 3D shapes and meshes. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper proposes a generative modelling approach. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with learning to generate and reconstruct 3D shapes. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with using shading information during training.
